Package: cairomm1
Version: 1.2.2
Revision: 1021
Description: C++ interface for the cairo library
License: LGPL
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <cairomm1@fink.racoonfink.com>

Depends: %N-shlibs (= %v-%r)
BuildDepends: cairo (>= 1.2-1), fontconfig1-dev, freetype219, glitz (>= 0.5.6-1), libgl-dev, libpng3, pkgconfig (>= 0.21-1), x11-dev, xft2-dev
GCC: 4.0

Source: http://cairographics.org/releases/cairomm-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: fabb040a5ff2cf0529af55ff46d22d2d

SetCFLAGS: -Os
SetCPPFLAGS: -I%p/lib/freetype219/include -I%p/lib/freetype219/include/freetype2 -I/usr/X11R6/include
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib/freetype219/lib
SetLIBS: -L/usr/X11R6/lib -L%p/lib
NoSetCFLAGS: true
NoSetCPPFLAGS: true
NoSetLDFLAGS: true
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man --disable-dependency-tracking PKG_CONFIG_PATH="%p/lib/freetype219/lib/pkgconfig:$PKG_CONFIG_PATH"

InstallScript: <<
#!/bin/sh -ev

	make install DESTDIR="%d"
	install -d -m 755 %i/share/doc/%N
	mv docs/reference examples %i/share/doc/%N/
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL MAINTAINERS NEWS README TODO
SplitOff: <<
	Package: %N-shlibs
	Depends: cairo-shlibs (>= 1.2.2-1001)
	DocFiles: COPYING
	Files: lib/lib*.*.*.dylib
	Shlibs: <<
		%p/lib/libglibmm-2.4.1.dylib 2.0.0 %n (>= 2.6.1-1)
		%p/lib/libglibmm_generate_extra_defs-2.4.1.dylib 2.0.0 %n (>= 2.6.1-1)
	<<
<<

Homepage: http://cairographics.org/

